{"tid":2279034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"輝瑞：強調有效數據非常初步 尚未被美國監管機構核實","createTime":"2020-11-09T13:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T14:20:22.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0cdd11dedf39d4465990ea26e04485326e5d0dd5","tid":2279034,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:29:09.000Z","msg":"輝瑞：初步數據顯示測試中疫苗有效但不表示短期可面世<br />\n<br />\n藥商輝瑞表示，初步數據顯示，測試中的新冠病毒疫苗有效，但強調不表示短期內疫苗可以面世。<br />\n<br />\n輝瑞指出，初步數據顯示，疫苗具備9成功效，可以預防新型肺炎，但強調數據非常初步。現時的數據有助向美國監管當局提出申請，在緊急情況下使用疫苗，進一步測試仍在進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559130-20201109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559130-20201109.htm&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y25ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=a37f2666\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559130-20201109.htm&h=65353e8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559130-20201109.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e4ba3e1db84db210ff08c6cb94510ca95a9c2bbd","tid":2279034,"uid":237425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"即係未撚用得? 又出黎鳩叫? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e875f0ecd968b46579e5f6cb06e8cc14901b5a1c","tid":2279034,"uid":25900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:33:19.000Z","msg":"未撚得咪出黎吠啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b364c80d315a8a779b49526556773a4039e8cd41","tid":2279034,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:35:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母  又造市"},{"pid":"7ed5c5832cb1b518debb0253423b45955f4956f7","tid":2279034,"uid":108337,"l